#: ../../utils.rst:2
msgid "Utilities"
msgstr "工具函数"

#: ../../utils.rst:4
msgid ""
"This module provides internal helper functions, video post-processing "
"effects, and progress-bar utilities. Most users do not need to interact with"
" these directly, but the public items are documented here for completeness."
msgstr "本模块提供内部辅助函数、视频后期处理效果和进度条工具。大多数用户无需直接使用这些功能，但为完整起见，此处对公开项进行了文档说明。"

#: ../../utils.rst:7
msgid "String processing"
msgstr "字符串处理"

#: ../../utils.rst:9
msgid ""
":func:`~.stripEmptyLines` — Remove leading and trailing empty lines from a "
"string."
msgstr ":func:`~.stripEmptyLines` — 移除字符串的首尾空行。"

#: ../../utils.rst:10
msgid ""
":func:`~.findSpacePositions` — Locate non-leading, non-trailing spaces in a "
"multi-line string."
msgstr ":func:`~.findSpacePositions` — 定位多行字符串中的非前导、非尾随空格。"

#: ../../utils.rst:11
msgid ""
":func:`~.replaceMiddleSpacesWithOccupyCharacter` — Replace middle spaces "
"with a placeholder character used by Manim."
msgstr ""
":func:`~.replaceMiddleSpacesWithOccupyCharacter` — 将中间空格替换为 Manim 使用的占位字符。"

#: ../../utils.rst:14
msgid "Video effects"
msgstr "视频效果"

#: ../../utils.rst:16
msgid ""
":func:`~.addGlowEffect` — Apply a soft-glow filter to a rendered video."
msgstr ":func:`~.addGlowEffect` — 对渲染后的视频应用柔光滤镜。"

#: ../../utils.rst:19
msgid "Progress bars"
msgstr "进度条"

#: ../../utils.rst:21
msgid ""
":class:`~.DefaultProgressBar` — A ``rich`` progress bar used during "
"rendering."
msgstr ":class:`~.DefaultProgressBar` — 渲染期间使用的 ``rich`` 进度条。"

#: ../../utils.rst:22
msgid ""
":class:`~.RichProgressBarLogger` — A ``proglog`` logger that bridges to Rich"
" progress bars."
msgstr ":class:`~.RichProgressBarLogger` — 桥接到 Rich 进度条的 ``proglog`` 日志记录器。"

#: ../../utils.rst:25
msgid "Context managers"
msgstr "上下文管理器"

#: ../../utils.rst:27
msgid ""
":func:`~.noManimOutput` — Suppress Manim console output within a ``with`` "
"block."
msgstr ":func:`~.noManimOutput` — 在 ``with`` 代码块内抑制 Manim 控制台输出。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.noManimOutput:1 of
msgid "Context manager used to execute code without outputting Manim logs."
msgstr "用于在不输出 Manim 日志的情况下执行代码的上下文管理器。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.noManimOutput:3 of
msgid ""
"Within the ``with`` block, Manim's standard output, standard error, and "
"progress bars are suppressed. Streams are restored when the block exits."
msgstr "在 ``with`` 代码块内，Manim 的标准输出、标准错误和进度条都会被抑制。代码块退出时流会恢复。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.noManimOutput of
msgid "Yields"
msgstr "生成"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.addGlowEffect:10
#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.noManimOutput:6 of
msgid "None"
msgstr "无"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.stripEmptyLines:1 of
msgid "Remove empty lines from the beginning and end of a string."
msgstr "移除字符串开头和结尾的空行。"

#: ../../utils.rst
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "参数"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.stripEmptyLines:3 of
msgid "The input string to process."
msgstr "要处理的输入字符串。"

#: ../../utils.rst
msgid "Returns"
msgstr "返回值"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.stripEmptyLines:6 of
msgid "The string with empty lines removed from the beginning and end."
msgstr "移除了开头和结尾空行后的字符串。"

#: ../../utils.rst
msgid "Return type"
msgstr "返回类型"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.typeName:1 of
msgid "Get the name of a type, handling union types and generic types."
msgstr "获取类型名称，支持联合类型和泛型。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.typeName:3 of
msgid "The type or value to get the name of."
msgstr "要获取名称的类型或值。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.typeName:5 of
msgid "The name of the type."
msgstr "类型名称。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.addGlowEffect:1 of
msgid "Add a glow effect to a video."
msgstr "为视频添加发光效果。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.addGlowEffect:3 of
msgid "Path to the input video file."
msgstr "输入视频文件的路径。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.addGlowEffect:5 of
msgid "Path to save the output video file."
msgstr "输出视频文件的保存路径。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.addGlowEffect:7 of
msgid "Whether to display progress bars."
msgstr "是否显示进度条。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.findSpacePositions:1 of
msgid ""
"Find the 2D positions of all non-leading, non-trailing spaces in a string. "
"Each position is represented as a list ``[row_index, column_index]``."
msgstr "查找字符串中所有非开头、非结尾的空格的二维位置。每个位置以列表 ``[row_index, column_index]`` 表示。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.findEmptyLinePositions:3
#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.findSpacePositions:4 of
msgid "A string."
msgstr "一个字符串。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.findSpacePositions:7 of
msgid ""
"A list of 2D positions of all non-leading, non-trailing spaces. Each "
"position is represented as a list ``[row_index, column_index]``."
msgstr "所有非开头、非结尾空格的二维位置列表。每个位置以列表 ``[row_index, column_index]`` 表示。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.findEmptyLinePositions:1 of
msgid "Find the line indices of all empty lines in a string."
msgstr "查找字符串中所有空行的行索引。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.findEmptyLinePositions:6 of
msgid "A list of line indices of all empty lines."
msgstr "所有空行的行索引列表。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.replaceMiddleSpacesWithOccupyCharacter:1 of
msgid ""
"Replace all non-leading, non-trailing spaces in the input string with "
":data:`~.OCCUPY_CHARACTER`. Retain leading and trailing spaces."
msgstr "将输入字符串中所有非开头、非结尾的空格替换为 :data:`~.OCCUPY_CHARACTER`。保留开头和结尾的空格。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.replaceMiddleSpacesWithOccupyCharacter:4 of
msgid "Original string."
msgstr "原始字符串。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.replaceMiddleSpacesWithOccupyCharacter:7 of
msgid ""
"Processed string with middle spaces replaced by :data:`~.OCCUPY_CHARACTER`."
msgstr "中间空格已被替换为 :data:`~.OCCUPY_CHARACTER` 的处理后字符串。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.DefaultProgressBar:1 of
msgid "Default progress bar used during video rendering."
msgstr "视频渲染期间使用的默认进度条。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.DefaultProgressBar:3 of
msgid ""
"This is a thin wrapper around ``rich.progress.Progress`` pre-configured with"
" descriptive columns (task name, bar, completion count, percentage, time "
"remaining, and transfer speed)."
msgstr ""
"这是对 ``rich.progress.Progress`` 的轻量包装，预配置了描述性列（任务名称、进度条、完成计数、百分比、剩余时间和传输速度）。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.RichProgressBarLogger:1 of
msgid "A progress logger that uses Rich to display progress bars."
msgstr "使用 Rich 显示进度条的进度记录器。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.RichProgressBarLogger:3 of
msgid ""
"This class bridges ``proglog`` (used by MoviePy) and ``rich`` progress bars,"
" allowing the glow-effect post-processing step to show a native-looking "
"progress indicator in the terminal."
msgstr ""
"此类桥接 ``proglog``\\ （MoviePy 使用）和 ``rich`` 进度条，使柔光效果后期处理步骤能够在终端中显示原生外观的进度指示器。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.RichProgressBarLogger.new_tqdm_bar:1 of
msgid "Create a Rich progress bar task for the given bar."
msgstr "为给定的进度条创建 Rich 进度条任务。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.RichProgressBarLogger.close_tqdm_bar:1 of
msgid "Close the Rich progress bar task for the given bar."
msgstr "关闭给定进度条的 Rich 进度条任务。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.RichProgressBarLogger.bars_callback:1 of
msgid "Update the Rich progress bar task based on the attribute change."
msgstr "根据属性变化更新 Rich 进度条任务。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.utils.RichProgressBarLogger.stop:1 of
msgid "Stop the Rich progress bar."
msgstr "停止 Rich 进度条。"
